{"tid":1450203,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日入機場既手足可以留意","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T22:54:45.000Z","uid":11489,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d52185c115877333d73de073bf402edc8a459a8","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以同旅客解釋 <br />\n我地唔係想阻住佢係機場抗爭<br />\n<br />\n只不過機場係我地唯一可以係和平安全既情況下集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再文宣話比佢聽出面叫遊行集會叫口號會比警犬亂放TG、射殺同拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我地先會入黎機場<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587190f2cc72ebcb4987b366ee356e7536b70aa3","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73647a61e35b1e02a8e4b75cca83a6c3a5e5ee4d","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"推x2"},{"pid":"f11fa47207a0a42fd3741139d2e3fc97ad9194eb","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:25.000Z","msg":"推x3"},{"pid":"8c49c4b983c1775f4cb68083a2600bbe059a34db","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:37.000Z","msg":"推x4"},{"pid":"8476e2a0268e15ccede00ccaa0058287cfba0444","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:49.000Z","msg":"推x5"},{"pid":"69ff5d673f37a997f493c406f0eabf82b2cd5c7a","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:14:03.000Z","msg":"推x6"},{"pid":"7696095c44bccb7f84ee003870179ff29a5a9f7c","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:14:15.000Z","msg":"推x7"},{"pid":"b03b6736e64028ccc9496a0b6be31b8428253d71","tid":1450203,"uid":11489,"like":0,"di